    <div id="pnlAddWord" style="display: none">
        

<div id="88fdb87a6e974fe69b431f5fcb9ad7f5" class="translate-form form-horizontal">
    <div class="form-group row" style="margin-bottom: 5px">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
            <input type="search" class="txt-translate form-control" placeholder="Enter word..." style="max-width: inherit" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <div class="translate-content">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<script type="text/javascript">
    (function() {
        var form = $('#88fdb87a6e974fe69b431f5fcb9ad7f5');
        var pnlTranslate = $('.translate-content', form);
        var txtTranslate = $('.txt-translate', form);
        var prefEnabled = 'True' == 'True';
        var contentLng = 'En';
        var limitExceeded = false;

        if (limitExceeded) {
            $(window).trigger('translate-changed', [form, '', true]);
        }

        $(form).on('click', '.btn-replace-translation', function() {
            txtTranslate.val($(this).html());

            $(this).closest('.pnl-change-translation').hide();
        });

        $(form).on('change', '.translate-content input', function () {
            $(window).trigger('translation-pref-changed', [form]);
        });

        $(form).on('click', '.btn-edit-translation', function() {
            var mainTranslationEl = $(this).closest('.main-translation');
            mainTranslationEl.addClass('main-translation-edit');
            $('.txt-main-translation', mainTranslationEl).focus();
        });

        function changeMainTranslation(el) {
            var mainTranslationEl = $(el).closest('.main-translation');
            mainTranslationEl.removeClass('main-translation-edit');

            var newTranslation = $('.txt-main-translation', mainTranslationEl).val();
            $('.main-translation-text', mainTranslationEl).text(newTranslation);

            $(window).trigger('translation-pref-changed', [form]);
        };

        $(form).on('click', '.btn-edit-translation-save', function () {
            changeMainTranslation(this);
        });

        $(form).on('keypress', '.txt-main-translation', function (e) {
            var keycode = (e.keyCode ? e.keyCode : e.which);
            if (keycode == '13') {
                changeMainTranslation(this);
            }
        });

        function translate(text) {
            pnlTranslate.empty();

            var loading = pnlTranslate.loadingIndicator();

            $.ajax({
                url: '/Home/WordDetail',
                data: { word: text, groupId: '1359bf0c883d4fd98b2cc82e2813cc91', changePref: prefEnabled, lng: contentLng },
                type: 'POST',
                complete: function() {
                    loading.hide();
                },
                success: function(html) {
                    var currentText = txtTranslate.val();

                    if (currentText == text) {
                        pnlTranslate.html(html);
                    }

                    var backTranslate = ($('input[name=txtBackTranslate]', pnlTranslate).val() || "false").toLowerCase() == "true";
                    var limitExceeded = ($('input[name=txtTranslationsLimit]', pnlTranslate).val() || "false").toLowerCase() == "true";

                    $(window).trigger('translate-changed', [form, text, backTranslate || limitExceeded]);
                },
                error: function() {
                    var currentText = txtTranslate.val();

                    if (currentText == text) {
                        pnlTranslate.html('Error. Please try again later.');
                    }

                    $(window).trigger('translate-changed', [form, text, true]);
                }
            });
        };

        txtTranslate.defferedBind('keyup', 1000, function (e) {
            e.stopPropagation();
            e.preventDefault();

            var text = $(this).val();
            if (text.length > 1) {
                translate(text);
            }
            else {
                pnlTranslate.empty();
                $(window).trigger('translate-changed', [form, text, true]);
            }
        });
    })();
</script>

    </div>


    
</body>
</html>
